BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 205.2 670 Td (Conditionals: If/Then) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 580 Td (Conditionals let programs make decisions! IF something is true, THEN do) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 562 Td (this. ELSE do that. Your brain uses conditionals all day: IF it is raining,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 544 Td (THEN take an umbrella. IF the light is red, THEN stop, ELSE go. Without) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 526 Td (conditionals, programs would do the same thing every time, no matter what.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 508 Td (Conditionals make programs smart and responsive.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 12 Tf 72 465 Td (KEY CONCEPT:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 90 445 Td (IF \(condition is true\) THEN \(do action A\) ELSE \(do action B\). You can also) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 90 427 Td (chain: IF...ELSE IF...ELSE for multiple options.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
