BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 580 Td (Artificial Intelligence \(AI\) is when computers learn from data instead of) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 562 Td (just following instructions. Regular programs do exactly what you tell) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 544 Td (them. AI programs learn patterns and make predictions! When Netflix) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 526 Td (suggests shows or your phone autocorrects words, that is AI. AI learns from) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 508 Td (LOTS of examples - like how you learned to recognize cats by seeing) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 490 Td (thousands of cats.) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 12 Tf 72 447 Td (KEY CONCEPT:) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 90 427 Td (AI needs: 1\) Lots of data \(examples\), 2\) A learning algorithm, 3\) Computing) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 11 Tf 90 409 Td (power. AI is not magic - it is math and patterns!) Tj ET

